author: mgiongco
title: Lady Eagles overcome Lady Tamaraws in 5 sets
text: INQUIRER.net / 06:28 PM February 12, 2017 FILE – Ateneo Lady Eagles. Tristan Tamayo/INQUIRER.net Ateneo rallied past a persistent Far Eastern University side, 25-19, 24-26, 19-25, 25-16, 15-11, for its second win in the UAAP Season 79 women’s volleyball tournament Sunday at Filoil Flying V Centre in San Juan. The Lady Eagles improved to 2-1 while the Lady Tamaraws slipped to 1-2. ADVERTISEMENT
